CSPA is the KL divergence  between (predictions after applying CSPA) and (original predictions). DMA is the KL divergence between (predictions after mean-ablating) and (original predictions). Each point is the average of a bunch of these values (we&#39;ve grouped according to the value of DMA). In other words, each (x, y) point on this graph represents (average KL div from mean ablating, average KL div from CSPA) for a group of points. The line is extremely close to the x-axis, showing that copy suppression is a good description of what this head is doing. </p><figure><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/JsquluPQa52r7xqdOxjYwLVEygFONGo-sCilbjjbJ1U=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9ibmxrMGVydTY5dGppczNlMmkxdg==" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/u8ABJ8wGcEiGdDdUdtVDd8LlZR-kUGSv09bluZ_SX1k=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9vMmp0NTh2ZG02MHJscG9uOThwaw== 100w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/s9p-u_D_c0qYGWthvJiw9UPFbhFcYEISoEyI1yD4-LM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9iejl2eWs0cGJqbXd4dHMzZmpoYQ== 200w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/g8hvDGwVYZuXdgAyG1NUH4SfEaq62KudN_8iE776shc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9tb2JxMHp1Y2s0aWh6YWVlcHdzOA== 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/7T8ApjgiJwa_pIrIUKmvO4JMFNktanFIMqOX5i9VLik=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9sN29hanVuOXFyenZ2ZjV2ZzNqZQ== 400w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/yb7MKynyAijMRjjUsVxzK4NMegWVKNtkan0n8N-F7no=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS9