code>Obama</code>. This sounded a lot like copy suppression to us, so we compared the anti-induction scores to the copy suppression scores (measured by how much the indirect object token is suppressed in the IOI task), and we found a strong correlation in the quadrant where both scores were positive:</p><figure><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/YYMoa_HJw5ETx7MFUOy1qYq37QFu5dT7F13wSo-iboU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9wMHVxbzFodGFkdmdjdGp1aXh5ZQ==" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/QLBt5mKnBV_6T4hA4zIUObHI1FX1snv6mU-x9Uq5Yts=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9kY2Rxa294cDJ3ZHVpYTNsb3k0ZQ== 170w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/n1U1Nfh9shxJsqlvYvafUHyo-DJevRtqeA7NSdDVta0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9pY2QyYnBmMG1ua3d1ZTVmZmp4cQ== 340w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/9siHoPHfq60Jd1NKIr5bHm3XJu98zmktyQxf9YuYwb0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9qZm0xMmh6NWFiZXFpdmx3M3FlbA== 510w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/5KQZTR5QqCEnztQVoKmWN18FX61a2OAeynJWc1L9XdQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9qdnprOWxrcmNmZzAwMnA0cm1qcA== 680w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Fxba1B5It1QQNsZx4PzvQ5y1vCxzMNOQPU2bZOyl990=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9lYmV6c0hXNnFKd3hURmFzWC9rdHhlMDVkaHpqd2pwNGtmYWdzdQ== 850w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/G_qFbZHHnLVNgsbpp_YVk0xglcHu3hfKVOdLUM2lGbo=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQ